data.description: Welcome to 82 SE 40th Lane in Lamar, MO--where country charm meets modern comfort! This delightful property sprawls across 6.6 acres of picturesque land, offering you a serene escape from the hustle and bustle. Step inside this 3460 square feet home and experience the perfect blend of coziness and functionality. The spacious kitchen, equipped with modern appliances and ample counter space, beckons you to create culinary masterpieces while enjoying the warmth of home. An additional workshop awaits your creative touch--a perfect space for turning dreams into reality or pursuing your hobbies with passion.Picture yourself strolling through your expansive backyard, envisioning gardens, a pool, or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. Reach out to schedule your showing today!
